CallFire,is,an,online,text,and,voice,messaging,platform,designed,to,meet,the,needs,of,a,variety,of,users,and,organizations,The,platform,comes,with,APIs,for,integrating,its,functions,into,third,party,applications,and,services,The,Text,Broadcast,API,allows,users,to,send,text,messages,from,their,digit,CallFire,phone,numbers,Examples,of,API,usage,are,provided,in,PHP